package.name: python-ctypes
package.summary: Advanced Foreign Function Interface for Python
package.description: ctypes is an advanced ffi (Foreign Function Interface) package for Python 2.3 and higher. ctypes allows to call functions exposed from dlls/shared libraries and has extensive facilities to create, access and manipulate simple and complicated C data types in Python - in other words: wrap libraries in pure Python. It is even possible to implement C callback functions in pure Python.

package.name: biosdevname
package.summary: Udev helper for naming devices per BIOS names
package.description: biosdevname in its simplest form takes a kernel device name as an argument, and returns the BIOS-given name it "should" be. This is necessary on systems where the BIOS name for a given device (e.g. the label on the chassis is "Gb1") doesn't map directly and obviously to the kernel name (e.g. eth0).

package.name: cppunit
package.summary: C++ unit testing framework
package.description: CppUnit is the C++ port of the famous JUnit framework for unit testing. Test output is in XML for automatic testing and GUI based for supervised tests.

package.name: cppunit-devel
package.summary: Libraries and headers for cppunit development
package.description: This package contains the libraries and headers necessary for developing programs that use cppunit.

package.name: cppunit-doc
package.summary: HTML formatted API documention for cppunit
package.description: The cppunit-doc package contains HTML formatted API documention generated by the popular doxygen documentation generation tool.

package.name: firmware-addon-dell
package.summary: A firmware-tools plugin to handle BIOS/Firmware for Dell systems
package.description: The firmware-addon-dell package provides plugins to firmware-tools which enable BIOS updates for Dell system, plus pulls in standard inventory modules applicable to most Dell systems.

package.name: libsmbios
package.summary: Libsmbios C/C++ shared libraries
package.description:
Libsmbios is a library and utilities that can be used by client programs to get information from standard BIOS tables, such as the SMBIOS table.
This package provides the C-based libsmbios library, with a C interface.
This package also has a C++-based library, with a C++ interface. It is not actively maintained, but provided for backwards compatibility. New programs should use the libsmbios C interface.

package.name: libsmbios-devel
package.summary: Development headers and archives
package.description:
Libsmbios is a library and utilities that can be used by client programs to get information from standard BIOS tables, such as the SMBIOS table.
This package contains the headers and .a files necessary to compile new client programs against libsmbios.

package.name: python-smbios
package.summary: Python interface to Libsmbios C library
package.description: This package provides a Python interface to libsmbios

package.name: smbios-utils
package.summary: Meta-package that pulls in all smbios binaries and python scripts
package.description: This is a meta-package that pulls in the binary libsmbios executables as well as the python executables.

package.name: smbios-utils-bin
package.summary: Binary utilities that use libsmbios
package.description: Get BIOS information, such as System product name, product id, service tag and asset tag.

package.name: smbios-utils-python
package.summary: Python executables that use libsmbios
package.description: Get BIOS information, such as System product name, product id, service tag and asset tag. Set service and asset tags on Dell machines. Manipulate wireless cards/bluetooth on Dell laptops. Set BIOS password on select Dell systems. Update BIOS on select Dell systems. Set LCD brightness on select Dell laptops.

package.name: yum-dellsysid
package.summary: YUM plugin to retrieve the Dell System ID
package.description:
Libsmbios is a library and utilities that can be used by client programs to get information from standard BIOS tables, such as the SMBIOS table.
This package contains a YUM plugin which allows the use of certain substitutions in yum repository configuration files on Dell systems.

package.name: firmware-usb-autoupdate
package.summary: Automatically update BIOS when USB Key with update is inserted
package.description: Provides HAL framework for detecting USB key insertion, finding BIOS updates on the USB key, and updating the BIOS automatically. Can also be configured to ask the user for confirmation.

package.name: dell-community-repository
package.summary: Repository configuration for the community repos at http://linux.dell.com/repo/community/
package.description:
The linux.dell.com community software repository contains unofficial and unsupported Dell-developed software, as well as customer-contributed open source software.
This package contains the yum-configuration for the linux.dell.com/repo/community/ repository.

package.name: dell-config-cluster
package.summary: Dell | Red Hat HA Cluster configuration utility
package.description: The dell-config-cluster utility will assist in deploying small (2-16) node Dell HA clusters connected to Dell storage. All Dell specific components such as DRAC and storage are configured and used for fencing devices where appropriate.

package.name: dkms
package.summary: Dynamic Kernel Module Support Framework
package.description: This package contains the framework for the Dynamic Kernel Module Support (DKMS) method for installing module RPMS as originally developed by Dell.
